c2d9280?r=3D9p0gt ] for editing, and to Chris, Bruno, Nat, Nathan, Jb, Luca=
s, Tom, Gabriel, 4484, Nathan, B
en, Alexander, and Jonny from Farcaster for ideas and resources!
That=E2=80=99s all for today. See you back here Friday for your Weekly Dose=
 of Optimism. Have a great week.
Thanks for reading,
Packy

